    {
      "parameters": {
        "content": "\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n## Transcript Getter\n\n**Supadata**  is an official Paid AI  service Provider which you can use for many services like You can get the metadata , Transcript , Scrape , Crawl , Map , etc on you any Videos [Supadata](https://docs.supadata.ai/)",
